{"tid":1579821,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"美式足球訓練方式 應對被狗咬","createTime":"2019-09-18T18:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T02:48:01.000Z","uid":268781,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c15040fd86c4f6fda4c318cc78d1d45e70a3c6f0","tid":1579821,"uid":268781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T18:17:09.000Z","msg":"首先，個人見解美式足球就係結合速度與力量，而大多數前線身體素質是沒有對抗性、持續性、爆發性同埋靈活性。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kfU_vJGBGxk(訓練方式參考\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkfU_vJGBGxk%28%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%83%E8%80%83&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=dd32cc45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kfU_vJGBGxk(訓練方式參考</a>)<br />\n以我所知美式足球係著重爆發性， 當你被狗拉，因為你既肌肉同對抗能力不足往往被狗一野拉低。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1fm48I3_wPk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1fm48I3_wPk&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=d08bc431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1fm48I3_wPk</a><br />\n同埋美式足球都著重靈活性同埋反應力，點解咁大隻既人又咁有靈活性係因為佢地著重步法訓練， 例如用敏捷梯。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xAUlx0eJ9eQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxAUlx0eJ9eQ&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=884a26d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xAUlx0eJ9eQ</a><br />\n<br />\n最後喇，我覺得應該需要一樣能力練到極致， 唔打得都跑得，人人都可以係美式足球員。"},{"pid":"b2f867c84cc835eb1913fe23015a5e15b6b68654","tid":1579821,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T18:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8sQjh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8sQjh3.jpg&h=ec6865d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【赤納粹賀壽系列】10.1 讓燭光燃點維港 <br />\n晚上8點 維多利亞港 <br />\n悼念太子831死者&amp;新屋嶺義士 <br />\n毋忘天安門八九六四民運遇難者 <br />\n <br />\n10.1 8點 維港見<br />\n<br />\n《自由花》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5GyryRRL-NY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5GyryRRL-NY&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=7c36f220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5GyryRRL-NY</a><br />\n<br />\n《血染的風采》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utvG-uwDsD8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DutvG-uwDsD8&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=021d1b05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utvG-uwDsD8</a><br />\n<br />\n《血染的風采》－習維尼老婆彭麗媛版<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=weKJw49svKA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DweKJw49svKA&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=febf8386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=weKJw49svKA</a>"},{"pid":"7c597ed6cca329154af2b96ee4be0067eb55f87e","tid":1579821,"uid":310898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T18:28:44.000Z","msg":"唔好覺得遲咗練、長期戰爭，練完點都有用，推"},{"pid":"b0d983595a3481dc4f4d68e8d50376d6afac1a90","tid":1579821,"uid":6111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T18:44:08.000Z","msg":"前線手足要練 後排和理非手足更加要練<br />\n你諗下 如果你地跑得夠快 有氣跑得更遠既話<br />\n咁前線勇武手足就唔洗因爲你地跑唔郁而硬食班加既衝擊<br />\n咁到時我地每次出去就可以0犧牲返屋企<br />\n好喇 或者你會自私d咁諗 我企後排走唔郁都冇辦法<br />\n反正唔會比狗咬 但你又諗下<br />\n勇武手足係現場就可以保到你 但如果你地返緊屋企果陣遇到福建幫呢？<br />\n到時除左你自己就冇人救到你<br />\n所以大家一定要練下個身體黎應付所有突發既事"},{"pid":"a71cde6e9eb7705401f295f7c1338360cfd154bf","tid":1579821,"uid":165425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T18:45:48.000Z","msg":"其實rugby會平民加實用啲，討論下"},{"pid":"f4d0f114c05e70c280afb8bd8e8c0aafff023b3e","tid":1579821,"uid":38662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T18:58:13.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"41d8a43cd421c4434a08f51c3099c3ee68cdba55","tid":1579821,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:46:27.000Z","msg":